Package com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy

com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy contains all functionalities of the taxonomy service. Provided functionalities are creation and deletion of application version taxonomy class mappings.

Produced Events via Outbox Pattern (topic: event type):

  • android-application: android_application_version_taxonomy_class_added
  • android-application: android_application_version_taxonomy_class_deleted
  • ios-application: ios_application_version_taxonomy_class_added
  • ios-application: ios_application_version_taxonomy_class_deleted
  • private-application: private_application_version_taxonomy_class_added
  • private-application: private_application_version_taxonomy_class_deleted

Consumed Events (topic: event type):

  • android-application: android_application_added
  • android-application: android_application_changed
  • android-application: android_application_version_added
  • android-application: android_application_version_changed
  • android-application: android_application_deleted
  • ios-application: ios_application_added
  • ios-application: ios_application_changed
  • ios-application: ios_application_version_added
  • ios-application: ios_application_version_changed
  • ios-application: ios_application_deleted
  • private-application: private_application_added
  • private-application: private_application_changed
  • private-application: private_application_version_added
